data.meta_description: Nia Long (born October 30, 1970) is an American actress best known for her roles in TV, on the series "Fresh Prince of Bel-Air" and "Third Watch." She's also appeared in the movies "Soul Food" and "Big Momma's House." Find more pictures and articles about Nia Long here.  Born: Nia Talita Long (1970-10-30) October 30, 1970 (age 49) Brooklyn, New York, U.S. Occupation: Actress Years active: 1986–present Partner(s): Massai Dorsey (1999–2001; ex-fiancé) Ime Udoka (2010–present; fiancé) Children: 2 Relatives: Sommore (half-sister)
